				</ukm:Metadata><Secondary><Body DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/body" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/body" NumberOfProvisions="133" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-30"><Part DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/part/6" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/part/6" NumberOfProvisions="35" id="part-6" RestrictStartDate="2025-07-22"><Number><Strong>PART 6</Strong></Number><Title>CALCULATION OF CAPITAL AND INCOME</Title><Chapter DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/part/6/chapter/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/part/6/chapter/1" NumberOfProvisions="6" id="part-6-chapter-1" RestrictStartDate="2013-04-29"><Number>CHAPTER 1</Number><Title>CAPITAL</Title><P1group RestrictStartDate="2013-04-29"><Title>Capital disregarded</Title><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/48" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/48" id="regulation-48">
<Pnumber>48</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/48/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/48/1" id="regulation-48-1">
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Any capital specified in Schedule 10 is to be disregarded from the calculation of a person's capital (see also regulations 75 to 77).</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/48/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/48/2" id="regulation-48-2">
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Where a period of 6 months is specified in that Schedule, that period may be extended by the Secretary of State where it is reasonable to do so in the circumstances of the case.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
</P1></P1group></Chapter></Part></Body></Secondary></Legislation>